  <summary date="2021-09-23T19:35:29Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Clean Commute for Kids Act of 2021

This bill reauthorizes through FY2031 and revises the Clean School Bus Program. Under the revised program, the Environmental Protection Agency must provide financial assistance to replace existing school buses with clean school buses that do not emit specified pollutants, including greenhouse gases.</summary>
